{
  "stem": "18575.2",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And he lived with them.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "She had two sons, and-- which I'll speak perhaps later.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And he taught the whole family Hebrew.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE] But I said he also taught religion or-- or the Bible.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But he was himself an atheist.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I had fights all the time.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We had kids, you know, that called us names.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They would start a fight.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I fought with every one of them.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I remember once I hit a kid that-- that was-- that got me-- kicked me badly, that his head went through a little window.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They had doors with those little windows.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE] through it.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "He got cut all together, but he didn't complain.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "He said it was accident.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "He was ashamed to-- to say that a Jewish boy knocked him out, so.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He only-- the only one-- of course, the priest, several times mentioned, you know, the killing of Christ, you know, the responsibility, the Jews, you know, the evil nations, evil people, things of that sort, you know, not paying attention there a few Jewish boys there.",
      "word_count": 46
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But we had a French teacher and a good one.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "In fact, we were forced to talk, in the first class, French.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But he would-- they had an expression in French that if you translate exactly it's not correct Polish.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he would say, that's the way the Jew talks.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "That's not Polish, you know, things of that sort.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The only thing we knew about Hitler prior of to the war-- I mean, I'm talking to a year or two year prior to the World War-- we knew of the Kristallnacht, of the pogroms that we called in Germany.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And there were-- I know of a family that run away or were expelled from Germany that came and lived in the apartment house.",
      "word_count": 24
    }
  ],
